.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F10%2Fjerry-falwell-jr-has-a-free-speech-problem%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--facebook" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Facebook" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F10%2Fjerry-falwell-jr-has-a-free-speech-problem%2F&text=.%40JerryFalwellJr+thinks+two+reporters%27+coverage+was+unfair%E2%80%94so+he+wants+them+arrested.&via=reason" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--twitter" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Twitter" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F10%2Fjerry-falwell-jr-has-a-free-speech-problem%2F&title=.%40JerryFalwellJr+thinks+two+reporters%27+coverage+was+unfair%E2%80%94so+he+wants+them+arrested." target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--reddit" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Reddit" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-reddit"></i></a><a href="mailto:?subject=Shared+From+Reason.com%3A+.%40JerryFalwellJr+thinks+two+reporters%27+coverage+was+unfair%E2%80%94so+he+wants+them+arrested.&body=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F04%2F10%2Fjerry-falwell-jr-has-a-free-speech-problem%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--email" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Email" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a><a href="https://reason.com/2020/04/10/jerry-falwell-jr-has-a-free-speech-problem/printer/" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social-